{"title":"Insulinoma-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/Insulinoma-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Insulinoma","guid":"DpVjVagBudxpmxkD_C7qdQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Introducción","guid":"guQaEKod2GECVSgvYbYV4A","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Hipoglucemia reconocida como característica\\Nde varias enfermedades en el siglo XIX.","guid":"lo3B9efBT91iJyLM4pMK-w","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• Insulina disponible para el tratamiento de la DM en los años 1920 ➜ eventos\\Nclínicos similares al sobretratamiento con insulina en individuos sin diabetes.","guid":"MvQLnP4uYjS66TUXBA-FRA","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"• Observación ➜ postulación de una nueva entidad: hiperinsulinismo (1).","guid":"WNo6j3H5rpO0Nlmbs0nZkw","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"• 1927: Descubrimiento de un tumor maligno de células de los islotes\\Npancreáticos en un paciente con episodios de hipoglucemia severa (2).","guid":"CLcHTqIW_2HmmwkA5LIraQ","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"• Extractos del tumor ➜ hipoglucemia marcada en conejos.","guid":"IG6EN5YeVuA-Ehto2BXzOw","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"• 1929: Primera cura de hiperinsulinismo mediante la extirpación de un insulinoma (3).","guid":"2Jf5yk-znbDf9UehtgGkAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"Incidencia","guid":"Nqac4Uk-jqeLzSl-7BHwWQ","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"• Período de observación:\\N1927-1986 (Mayo Clinic)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"• 224 pacientes con insulinoma extirpado.","guid":"tm9Rc32GS1Tba3t_l9E0xw","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"• 8 casos en residentes de Olmsted County, Minnesota.","guid":"0MKoX5LCykyMQjNket_hWA","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"• Incidencia: 0.4 por 100,000 personas-año\\N(4 casos por millón de individuos por año)","guid":"3ax4tMiY4t3izIxpN3HJkA","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"8","text":"• Grupos étnicos:","guid":"E4yz73WZc5id8P_V0aQgwg","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• Insulinomas observados en todos los grupos étnicos.","guid":"C1Q6mzyPFU14StzYBOaNYA","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"8","text":"• Insulinomas\\Nreportados en:","guid":"-Js-E5lCTa91YEfF9bxy1Q","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"• Mujeres embarazadas.","guid":"r3kpvryKT7QCugT1oqOG0w","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"• Pacientes con DM2 (9,10).","guid":"r6S_E0v3Ez8tTtMNJvGYDg","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"15","text":"• 1 paciente con DM1 (11).","guid":"AKIeLvLMCVngmhDfhrfGCw","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"15","text":"• 1 paciente con ERC (12).","guid":"eaGh9GL142lVJ4Qbk2-gug","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"8","text":"Distribución de casos\\Npor edad y sexo","guid":"0bXegj_zjyTjdYMubAYtIw","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"• Serie\\N1987-2007:","guid":"wDQhMMpyZqz3O06-gKLtMw","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"• 237 pacientes.","guid":"Z2U9uSn9u05auh2UD0Ljuw","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"• Edad mediana: 50 años (rango: 17-86 años).","guid":"j6EWTf_8PbzNZHreo-9lKg","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"• 57% mujeres (4).","guid":"Lt1OTbHF6DfuoM6vbS-upA","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"20","text":"• Comparación con serie\\Nanterior (1927-1986):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• Hallazgos similares (8).","guid":"Zj0UJMBLxjQSC5iqcigpgw","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"20","text":"• Comparación con cohortes\\Nde otros estudios:","guid":"G9TytBi63fICeCg_IJ5v7A","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• Cohorte de 40 pacientes chinos con insulinoma (15\\Naños de estudio) → Hallazgos comparables (16).","guid":"srXrAUASNS5mfjSOJo_tPQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"0","text":"Clínica","guid":"EEzWjhWtUKUv106hrbWNdA","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Síntomas\\Nneuroglucopénicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• Confusión.","guid":"36JrmJfR3gpv4N_FDLPDag","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"• Cambios visuales.","guid":"EIbZlPDiBIMf1w9CiFwa9w","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"• Comportamiento inusual (13).","guid":"IcjTwOoDn2Bf7eT7irJPMg","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"30","text":"• Síntomas\\Nsimpato-adrenales:","guid":"Bf8uFiQG5resrmgiF36Bgw","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• Palpitaciones.","guid":"GtRCnN16caPfChUcCvh8FQ","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"• Diaforesis.","guid":"xD-tTvgzwTanMnIKFIqlCQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"34","text":"• Temblor (17).","guid":"ujx6fQmpiLuzITLJ6S021g","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"30","text":"• Amnesia:","guid":"TRVbuOIcSG0hJp_zSXxKjg","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• Común durante episodios hipoglucémicos.","guid":"tkDdZCQhDfzgLQ6bd5u2AA","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"30","text":"• Aumento de peso:","guid":"-lC6s-otOEUjsmibwZNWMg","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"• Descrito en 18% de pacientes (18).","guid":"tXCuiaGCoVLrH2sb4VVLqA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"29","text":"• Duración de síntomas\\Nantes del diagnóstico:","guid":"xaThw-StjlfqLYlQiW9c3w","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• Mediana < 1.5 años (8).","guid":"CNXbaaffm4_9m0URzmlhCQ","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"• Algunos pacientes sintomáticos por décadas.","guid":"LCSsTRDAezTU_O3x5FNA-w","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"29","text":"• Estado de aparición\\Nde síntomas:","guid":"4n9qPoKJ8J7_N3teGuJIIg","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"• Exclusivamente en ayuno: 73% de pacientes.","guid":"S-FlzYGR5mHbwwu8hPHmdg","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"• Ayuno y postprandial: 21% de pacientes.","guid":"ZyTD0Wew357hqpA_-DQNzg","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"• Solo postprandial: 6% de pacientes (4).","guid":"nuSdq1T6Tc5Ppyj2DioxXg","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"29","text":"• Frecuencia de síntomas\\Npostprandiales:","guid":"5bhpzkTVsS_56R5vySPekw","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"• Aumento del 2% (1987-1992) al 10% (2003-2007).","guid":"Qc731BWVAjBZGyoYDbPfsA","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"29","text":"• Diagnósticos\\Nerróneos:","guid":"5wUkaWPwr-IsiQt20SENOg","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"• Trastorno neurológico o psiquiátrico: hasta 20% de pacientes (13,18).","guid":"u8WrY1300vVAHAeE4sCbpQ","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"• Trastorno convulsivo: diagnóstico común erróneo (8,17).","guid":"kthWN4SgSynQEAD9HmRG5Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"0","text":"Insulinomas en\\Npacientes con MEN1","guid":"lKbrtywGSIt-RR_up-foUA","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"• Cohorte Mayo\\NClinic: 237 pacientes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• 14 pacientes (6%) con neoplasia endocrina múltiple tipo 1 (MEN1).","guid":"RZf6Y5og5_6n5FOI_hAcLg","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"• 71% de los pacientes con MEN1 eran hombres (4).","guid":"SmbZR1p18YdLmSTwaZ6how","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"54","text":"• Insulinomas en\\Npacientes con MEN1:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"• 13 pacientes (93%) con insulinomas benignos.","guid":"x4y_rciXfMbkZ8rIIHvNmQ","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"• 12 pacientes (86%) con múltiples tumores de islotes.","guid":"YfH6NmC85IMcFax2C_9e3A","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"54","text":"• Comparación con el resto de la cohorte:\\Nsolo 3% tenían múltiples tumores de islotes.","guid":"sJj1tYZo-PYKKTgFrPPiJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"0","text":"Características del\\Ntumor de insulinoma","guid":"2dXLML8vmprETDaWkdV9nw","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"• Insulinomas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"• Pueden ser únicos o múltiples.","guid":"rY-VcYwCCUkxD9fIfqyJfw","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"62","text":"• Benignos o malignos.","guid":"GymUlxeyOVVHGVMl_2pamQ","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"62","text":"• Cohorte de 224\\Npacientes (8):","guid":"3qkU6-JZs95pYOc-UNqpvg","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"• 194 (87%): Tumores benignos únicos (uno ectópico).","guid":"3UZ1eJ1kzj5BVrSdFB0RwQ","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"• 16 (7%): Tumores benignos múltiples.","guid":"ZRJzvH5xONf2xRIIogP-xA","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"66","text":"• 13 (6%): Insulinomas malignos (definidos por presencia de metástasis).","guid":"W89ZPyAgX4_rsSmK_qDrtg","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"66","text":"• 1: Hiperplasia de islotes (11).","guid":"Bf1NiQ0Zflz-OAGu-5TTKg","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"62","text":"• Edad mediana de pacientes\\Ncon insulinoma maligno:","guid":"GiJo_jxIPEZBAGwfjbmKgg","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"• 48 años (rango 18-61 años).","guid":"VhN8P7uhw2Oz467ICrovwg","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"• 77% hombres.","guid":"Tv4osQXf9SicKfCeB9qxrA","children":[]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"62","text":"• Pacientes con cirugía inicial fallida o\\Nenfermedad recurrente (1927-1986):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"• Prevalencia aumentada de MEN1 con tumores\\Nmúltiples (25%) y insulinomas malignos (13%) (8).","guid":"g3SlXUOVGeJsWO2OgAYNpg","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"• Estudio de 103 pacientes (90 benignos, 13 malignos) en 30 años:","guid":"QuBmp1tJjMXalF7HMDITmA","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"62","text":"• Características clínicas y criterios diagnósticos: No diferían entre enfermedad benigna y maligna (19).","guid":"ATuQqcbB5qzYAkhv1KeDjw","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico y\\Nestadificación","guid":"Z1rc4gWEmWD3aK3ydzd6uQ","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"• Diagnóstico de\\Ninsulinoma:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"• Demostración de concentraciones séricas de insulina inapropiadamente\\Naltas durante un episodio espontáneo o provocado de hipoglucemia.","guid":"13Ga2LbiK1yBrnv-vL69wQ","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"• Ejemplos:","guid":"mFomyR4SLvgOOH4ek7FXKA","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"• Ayuno de 72 horas para hipoglucemia en ayuno.","guid":"21wNbJ5pl4IWIXaZm3lTpA","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"• Prueba de comida mixta para síntomas postprandiales.","guid":"LSgAr2QMI7uWzIb1bUoFWQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"78","text":"• Tumores de células\\Nde los islotes:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"• La mayoría de los insulinomas son tumores de células de los islotes.","guid":"sC57X9uAA5YTV1iF3lWTng","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"• Caso reportado de carcinoma de células pequeñas\\Ndel cuello uterino secretor de insulina (20).","guid":"N4oQuRLb6uyvr7uwEF2nrg","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"78","text":"• Diferenciación de\\Notros tumores:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"• Diferenciar de tumores que producen hipoglucemia por\\Nmecanismos no mediados por insulina (ej., producción de IGF-2).","guid":"DvAGF8E5HImFUDa-ym6xuQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"78","text":"• Potencial\\Nmaligno:","guid":"S4xcYph9Gwlq2Ofla36lnA","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"• Insulinomas malignos raros.","guid":"fCnPlCyPUoE_VdVTvYwAbQ","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"• Presentación clínica y pronóstico a largo plazo limitados.","guid":"kUiyX6qdIXP1GpoNdNoSNQ","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"• Generalmente tumores indolentes.","guid":"ARCNCnfRRGkNdtNmXhyv0w","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"89","text":"• Supervivencia prolongada posible incluso con\\Nmetástasis hepáticas o en ganglios linfáticos.","guid":"koM8pfXzW-H-ysZCB7YxmQ","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"89","text":"• El comportamiento biológico no siempre\\Ncorresponde a características histológicas.","guid":"z0Zp71z4LfhMpRoqDTsr-w","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"78","text":"• Sistemas de estadificación\\Ny clasificación:","guid":"A0PeNo8att3c28LG6sAK4g","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"• Desarrollados para predecir resultados a largo plazo.","guid":"RIRD2pUvNPtLVQSZd7bsxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"78","text":"• Clasificación OMS para tumores neuroendocrinos\\Ngastroenteropancreáticos malignos:","guid":"GY_MgAeZfLii55WRe857Mg","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"• Basada en criterios relacionados con el estadio (tamaño del tumor <2 vs. >2 cm y presencia de\\Nmetástasis) y grado (tasa mitótica, invasión perineural y linfovascular, índice proliferativo Ki-67) (22).","guid":"CBktqMkU_eXVz6nS1EsZGA","children":[]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"78","text":"• Otro esquema de\\Nclasificación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"• Estima el potencial maligno usando criterios de estadificación similares pero un\\Nsistema de clasificación simplificado (tasa mitótica y presencia de necrosis) (23).","guid":"U0ROWXBjzGO_8fb4tJzb2A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico\\Ndiferencial de\\Ninsulinoma","guid":"O5M28oYvAuSMJoFk82vF5A","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"• PHHI (Hipoglucemia Hiperinsulinémica\\NPersistente de la Infancia):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"• También llamada hiperinsulinismo familiar o congénito.","guid":"eZYcSrGlR5qc3mTZPNkGMw","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"• Trastorno genético, generalmente autosómico recesivo,\\Npero se ha descrito herencia autosómica dominante.","guid":"diRzbxsqU9a5IQh0IJvf7A","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"101","text":"• NIPHS (Síndrome de Hipoglucemia\\NPancreatogénica No Insulinoma):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"• Presentación en adultos.","guid":"paiiPftb5k0KVx0CMmXQmw","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"• Caracterizado por hipertrofia de islotes.","guid":"DF44HZtKybeof6_aSvB5EA","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"• Hipoglucemia postprandial (2-4 horas después de la comida).","guid":"F5JETk1N77W_hxQnFmVpTg","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"• Hipoglucemia en ayuno rara.","guid":"xhAFRIVdpFKeNeVh0slMFw","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"101","text":"• Anomalías de islotes pancreáticos\\Npost-bypass gástrico:","guid":"M5oG7kx2xwlmteP3FB5VQA","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"• Descritas en hipoglucemia post-bypass gástrico.","guid":"1_DRl8fUEaprR1fN-qP2AQ","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"• Insulinoma muy raro en contexto post-cirugía bariátrica.","guid":"nB0GKMw19LY_HIp7qNTrOQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"101","text":"• Hipoglucemia inducida\\Npor sulfonilureas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"• Considerar en evaluación de hipoglucemia.","guid":"mB1rbmnOb97GhfYM4ps52A","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"• Patrón caótico de ocurrencia (no relacionado con comidas o ayuno).","guid":"k55Wgtza-X8E14-esXN_rg","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"113","text":"• Presentación clínica puede parecerse a insulinoma.","guid":"V05C1y1Y0z8cr4h7Gw_sJQ","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"113","text":"• Evaluación bioquímica apropiada esencial\\Npara evitar exploración quirúrgica innecesaria.","guid":"-P4_jeH3-K4S7QX9yVt8WA","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"101","text":"• Hipoglucemia facticia por\\Nadministración exógena de insulina:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"• Insulina, C-péptido y proinsulina elevados en insulinoma.","guid":"FEPt8lJIutyaJWO14Qcz1g","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"• Insulina exógena: C-péptido y proinsulina\\Nsuprimidos, insulina elevada variablemente.","guid":"1HCDd2ZikISAOTTImETUsg","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"101","text":"• Trastornos de\\Nhipoglucemia autoinmune:","guid":"o4V20p0bu5_ARLXlFBj3Xg","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"• Anticuerpos dirigidos a insulina endógena o receptor de insulina.","guid":"I_-jsY1abiIoU8w_F6x1tA","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"• Síntomas postprandiales, en ayuno o ambos.","guid":"ukDFu-ny-_Jlo9ne1Pxtjw","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"• Hipoglucemia atribuida a unión transitoria inicial de insulina a\\Nautoanticuerpos, seguida de disociación no regulada.","guid":"jHb53tYXDtkIjxvacO-Etg","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"121","text":"• Anticuerpos al receptor de insulina causan\\Nactivación mediada por anticuerpos del receptor.","guid":"-v7gFhytjmPJ-EsM-2N6jA","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"121","text":"• Medición de anticuerpos de insulina o receptor\\Ndistingue hipoglucemia autoinmune de insulinoma.","guid":"oAlOvxunfFHSCLHI6YW0mw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"0","text":"Localización del\\Ntumor","guid":"bc_6S-wJT_ugJA14UopUeg","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"• Pruebas no\\Ninvasivas:","guid":"H0Mu1MDnBcsnwvKC7G6ntg","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"• Técnicas de imagen post\\Ndiagnóstico bioquímico:","guid":"KiAF3PSoWVWty6j6hPQvvQ","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"• Importancia: planificación quirúrgica y\\Nasesoramiento al paciente.","guid":"69Is3-yz0ChXjzROLJEp7g","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"• Algunos tumores no son\\Npalpables durante la cirugía (29).","guid":"JxYD9EvRcgauChqJPvEAOw","children":[]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"128","text":"• Procedimientos de\\Nimagen no invasivos:","guid":"rBai9Jm4yiPuTs8_sScclw","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"• TC helicoidal.","guid":"EScw4UQGSvNRGOGtDYzAbg","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"• RMN.","guid":"1SJ7AYtWxJhpQh1Q3xAzKg","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"132","text":"• Ecografía transabdominal.","guid":"SwCAbs47VV00GFNHC5Nm-A","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"132","text":"• Imagen con 111-In-pentetreotida.","guid":"0qkKwMYyUOHXIHo1ggEUfQ","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"132","text":"• PET con fluorina-18-L-dihidroxifenilalanina (18F-DOPA PET) (30,31).","guid":"b5Lh8ctbckY57mSMmAZP1Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"128","text":"• Elección del\\Nprocedimiento:","guid":"Unt-qBswQ20WEZ_zLsV4MA","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"• Depende de disponibilidad y experiencia radiológica local.","guid":"qvNO1mpAe7-NoRPvRsIW5g","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"• Pruebas iniciales\\Npreferidas:","guid":"6xCjwD0Di6n8l2ZIMbonLw","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"• Ecografía transabdominal.","guid":"nlZWG1hRCTU-OcJ-9ZKD0g","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"• TC helicoidal triple fase.","guid":"fQHkIi1iwSjpnH_3xXssNQ","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"140","text":"• Serie de 237 pacientes con\\Ninsulinoma (Mayo Clinic):","guid":"rtIfzeV-LB6UFAiZM5R_mQ","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"• Tasa de detección combinada: ecografía transabdominal y TC helicoidal\\Ntriple fase ≈ 70% (4).","guid":"PMhV7byWHf7sROBI0fey4g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"138","text":"• Opciones\\Nadicionales:","guid":"_QhixwcrK76-Dbt8h-Iusg","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"• PET/CT con Ga-68\\NDOTATATE:","guid":"Kwt9F8s3xFcdPW-fIkr3aw","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"• Utilizado cuando estudios convencionales\\Nno identifican el insulinoma.","guid":"CAYEre8sKQ6pjGKnAeEJLg","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"• Análisis retrospectivo de 31 pacientes:\\Ncorrecta localización en 9 de 10 pacientes.","guid":"wCYvzgZxrIOyeJDW-pPiLg","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"146","text":"• Expresión baja de receptores de somatostatina subtipo 2\\Nen insulinomas puede limitar detección (32).","guid":"L1OdGbavpWLYYYBaYxSRWQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"138","text":"• Concentraciones altas de\\Nreceptores de GLP-1:","guid":"eCp0UNZBAygXw9e-WUejKw","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"• Radioligandos de GLP-1:","guid":"vgH_wmQRchsqo5zHJDe6ng","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"• Escintigrafía de receptor de GLP-1.","guid":"kum0AaM1CeydrkuCabNZYw","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"150","text":"• Serie pequeña: localización exitosa en 6 pacientes (33).","guid":"n9_qmG4IIZHsOHN7F-Gi-Q","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"150","text":"• Necesidad de más investigación.","guid":"YxpgyfcqujSJ59-kk_--Pw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"127","text":"Pruebas\\Ninvasivas","guid":"u2UUWWFt9e1FERvV_0j82g","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"• Hipoglucemia hiperinsulinémica endógena.","guid":"SXjCEC8qPWQwIzHlfbxifQ","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"• Estudios de localización radiológicos no invasivos negativos.","guid":"9o-g9W_6heYJbV82nwkqnQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"155","text":"• Opciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"• Ultrasonografía endoscópica (USE).","guid":"Sus4VQSfLEO455XhpZx1Fg","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"• Prueba de estimulación arterial selectiva con calcio\\N(SACST) con muestreo venoso hepático (34,35).","guid":"7D88HwZML7S_sx5wCPhkyg","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"155","text":"• Tasa de identificación\\Nde tumores:","guid":"UHvlCkZXCleSCcGa3Jw35w","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"• 98% con estudios de localización preoperatorios\\Nadecuados + USE intraoperatoria y palpación.","guid":"znTPAw89hWdGYhT8cgoHHg","children":[]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"155","text":"• Ultrasonografía\\Nendoscópica (USE):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"• Serie de casos pequeños:\\Nsensibilidad 82-85% (34,36).","guid":"nQr-G-TztaQUq_8SRjyP2g","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"• Serie Mayo Clinic (237 pacientes):\\Nsensibilidad 75% (4).","guid":"RD4Le6yg8NsOpoW5zPVqrA","children":[]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"155","text":"• Prueba de estimulación arterial\\Nselectiva con calcio (SACST):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"• Prueba dinámica.","guid":"M7JAJz1irDQgAV57Y8LOlg","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"167","text":"• Inyección selectiva de gluconato de calcio en arterias\\Ngastroduodenal, esplénica y mesentérica superior.","guid":"87W-DJ7n3mgmBCCc-34QXw","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"167","text":"• Muestreo de efluente venoso\\Nhepático para insulina (35,37).","guid":"Jh55r0yoglS07LFGtA-6wQ","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"167","text":"• Observación: calcio estimula liberación de insulina de células beta hiperfuncionales\\N(insulinomas o nesidioblastosis) pero no de células beta normales.","guid":"GVQrnGxawda_XwAgK9UhTQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"155","text":"• Serie Mayo Clinic (237\\Npacientes): sensibilidad 93% (4).","guid":"73JOSpuqseZ-VHKwEa24tA","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"• Localización tumoral en todos los casos con pruebas no\\Ninvasivas negativas (ecografía, TC abdomen) desde 1998.","guid":"4auNCtq35mfHhnVQI9dorQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"174","parent":"155","text":"• Diferenciación de insulinoma\\Nvs. nesidioblastosis:","guid":"j2BFArZabWY43AbBius0vg","children":[{"id":"175","parent":"174","text":"• Revisión retrospectiva\\N(Mayo Clinic, 1996-2014):","guid":"YwksVGU4ZftBdBAwHMqaOg","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"• 116 casos de hipoglucemia hiperinsulinémica endógena\\Ny estudios no invasivos negativos o inconclusos.","guid":"nxe5-T7gZgB5jpHMJIsxFw","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"• 42 pacientes con insulinoma y 74 con\\Nnesidioblastosis confirmados por cirugía (38).","guid":"BbvPDuY0UAp5SopthyQW5Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"174","text":"• Criterios de\\NSACST:","guid":"0yo59dXCsZ9lpA2otoYQZQ","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"• Aumento máximo de insulina venosa hepática sobre\\Nla línea base después de inyección de calcio:","guid":"kRjTAowQa19sC3WTeyTXUQ","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"•  91.5 µU/mL y >263.5 µU/mL: 95% y 100%\\Nespecíficos para insulinoma, respectivamente.","guid":"7RjnHYyxsrtCt7QKIMOhAg","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"• Aumento 19 veces de insulina venosa hepática sobre la línea base:\\N99% específico para insulinoma.","guid":"zrNrqEn9bAC1T4MBHzZsdw","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"178","text":"• Respuesta robusta a calcio en una\\Narteria: sugestiva de insulinoma.","guid":"DQ-85y-sZalEGQoP9PF0IA","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"178","text":"• Respuesta modesta en más de una\\Narteria: compatible con nesidioblastosis.","guid":"CL0maY7C-NYeSq5A8t16Sg","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"178","text":"• Superposición en características de respuesta: sin criterio\\Nque proporcione precisión diagnóstica completa.","guid":"EevlHXQqOOcqpL0yFf2ktg","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"d6wpa8EbD1z3jqFedCXz8g","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"• Tratamiento de elección: extirpación\\Nquirúrgica del insulinoma.","guid":"LOqDvnK_fMuXVPRJLZKVTg","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"• Procedimientos realizados en la\\Ncohorte de Mayo Clinic (8):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"• Enucleación del insulinoma: 130 pacientes.","guid":"DKGjmrB7eE2DskGlKtqcRg","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"• Pancreatectomía distal parcial: 73 pacientes.","guid":"t7k-_9RV6W6NeKSYOItqsg","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"187","text":"• Enucleación del insulinoma + pancreatectomía parcial: 9 pacientes.","guid":"5A1GTdWj-MqyWue9xFSyMQ","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"187","text":"• Procedimiento de Whipple (extirpación de cabeza del páncreas,\\Ngastrectomía, duodenectomía, esplenectomía): 1 paciente.","guid":"41_Zu3TstRpxXk2TD6MR0g","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"187","text":"• Pancreatectomía total: 1 paciente.","guid":"AzPdroI74JaqTUPucKF94w","children":[]}]},{"id":"193","parent":"185","text":"• Elección del\\Nprocedimiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"• Determinada por el cirujano.","guid":"fAym5-VmZUU-ixUhoUYI2w","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"• Ninguna operación (1927-1986) fue laparoscópica; procedimientos\\Nlaparoscópicos realizados en pacientes seleccionados desde entonces.","guid":"cbvJi1Rx_wPHmxH2b60I4Q","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"193","text":"• Tasa de complicaciones quirúrgicas: ≈10%.","guid":"h3h15368CLgWAjBwWtF5FQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"185","text":"• Pacientes con\\Ninsulinomas malignos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"• Biopsia de lesiones metastásicas: 8 pacientes.","guid":"hNcq6GaEuOfK44jZ1627NQ","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"• Tumor identificado en autopsia tras muerte perioperatoria: 1 paciente.","guid":"EL8J3ZWDjPs-1zpbd3YuPg","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"197","text":"• Examen histológico: tumor de células de los islotes\\Nmaligno que tiñó intensamente para insulina.","guid":"j3WfLvVmCTlCAvQfJiqOXA","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"185","text":"• Resultados\\N(1927-1986) (8):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"• 196 pacientes (87.5%): curados (sin síntomas por\\N≥6 meses tras extirpación del insulinoma).","guid":"nZgEGzaGUEOikPPdlZL1LQ","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"201","text":"• 19 pacientes (8.5%; 10 con insulinomas benignos, 8 con insulinomas malignos,\\N1 con hiperplasia de células de los islotes): hipoglucemia persistente.","guid":"9bOLiY7blIFxpHB-a6U_pA","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"201","text":"• 5 pacientes (2.2%):\\Ndesarrollaron DM.","guid":"8bm4NrIMtn8QSHUudF2M2Q","children":[{"id":"205","parent":"204","text":"• 4 pacientes (1.8%): muerte\\Nperioperatoria (todos antes de 1941).","guid":"RXmsRJ7968hlaPGRwptcrw","children":[]}]},{"id":"206","parent":"201","text":"• Hipoglucemia persistente tras\\Ntratamiento quirúrgico inicial:","guid":"ih1Ed4kHbjc3Qscjs2Plnw","children":[{"id":"207","parent":"206","text":"• 10 pacientes con insulinomas benignos.","guid":"G3XvfVs8hOAuAuf6yVgjjQ","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"206","text":"• 6 tenían múltiples tumores (4 debido a MEN1).","guid":"XjFVE7Sq5fqWnNxMvfrHsw","children":[]}]},{"id":"209","parent":"201","text":"• 5 reoperados:","guid":"H4IMYKMI2-ACx4o5VHMcDg","children":[{"id":"210","parent":"209","text":"• 3 con tumores múltiples adicionales: 1 curado,\\N2 desarrollaron DM tras segunda operación.","guid":"POJpAdesArZoMnRHnpbY2Q","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"209","text":"• 2 pacientes con tumores únicos: hipoglucemia persistente tras\\Nsegunda operación (insulinomas adicionales no identificados).","guid":"iLqVjfKZLPuRBsmgXqmYpQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"212","parent":"201","text":"• Insulinoma\\Nrelacionado con\\NMEN1:","guid":"zoN3HIUpRPDx_NooUFgEWA","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"• Recomendación: excisión local de tumores en la cabeza\\Ndel páncreas + pancreatectomía subtotal distal.","guid":"FzJ6Q2InRXT1PB2eAUSkEg","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"• Diferencia con insulinomas esporádicos: generalmente un tumor\\Nsolitario, enucleación usualmente exitosa (39).","guid":"0q0PiC4drv9QDFaZ0tvK3w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"215","parent":"185","text":"Cirugía\\Nlaparoscópica","guid":"s0DB6Jo97QWP_Kn0sT7pNg","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"• Indicación:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"• Realizada en algunos centros para insulinomas pequeños y\\Nsolitarios localizados preoperatoriamente (40-42).","guid":"_9higMKVk_t1GZJI7ef5vA","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"216","text":"• Ultrasonografía laparoscópica intraoperatoria puede\\Nminimizar necesidad de conversión a cirugía abierta.","guid":"cWD6JkvqdxHpFExWMgY3wQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"215","text":"• Ablación química:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"• Inyección percutánea guiada por ecografía de etanol en insulinoma en\\Npacientes con alto riesgo quirúrgico → resolución de hipoglucemia (43).","guid":"g3lT6oZVaWzjKPr58n6c3Q","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"219","text":"• Inyección de agente esclerosante lauromacrogol:\\Nresolución de hipoglucemia en 7 pacientes (44).","guid":"8MRxx4sgpFoX50s77IdcAQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"215","text":"• Evaluación de insulinoma\\Nno detectado:","guid":"bqJyEEPI3hiu-_VAIpJghg","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"• Reconfirmación del diagnóstico.","guid":"VE4CnrstXgOhfnx5l8bQ4A","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"• Realización de procedimientos de\\Nlocalización antes de reoperación.","guid":"ubtiRbIA4jrwYxGE29tVww","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"222","text":"• Reoperación solo por cirujano experimentado,\\Ncon apoyo endocrinológico y radiológico.","guid":"Xq0xmPr7e7ZHiaJVSGOEhA","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"222","text":"• No realizar resección pancreática a\\Nciegas si los estudios de localización no\\Ndetectan el tumor (45).","guid":"wIZCnl5MHldbS7R31GeYRA","children":[]}]},{"id":"227","parent":"215","text":"• Riesgo de recurrencia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"228","parent":"227","text":"• Serie Mayo Clinic (1927-1986): 196 pacientes en remisión\\Nposquirúrgica, 11 (6%) con hipoglucemia recurrente.","guid":"XXTv9z04g1lpaYztkWIQUQ","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"227","text":"• 8 pacientes\\Nreexplorados:","guid":"SQNJFz5gRAVW8TtK4XpKQQ","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"• 6 con confirmación patológica de\\Ninsulinoma recurrente.","guid":"RZE2j2JpNqgkfd49TwBDvQ","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"229","text":"• 1 con hipoglucemia persistente\\Ntras pancreatectomía total.","guid":"gk-at1c8_0L-ap0RUmzo3g","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"229","text":"• 1 falleció\\Nintraoperatoriamente.","guid":"pFdwGIf2xzRk3aZOJhmJzg","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"229","text":"• Recurrencias entre 4-18.5 años\\Ntras la operación inicial.","guid":"06w2OZCppBsW1C7gw-pvIQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"234","parent":"227","text":"• Incidencia acumulada de recurrencia: 6% a 10 años, 8% a 20 años.","guid":"xkop44_S6ti8EexKKw4U7Q","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"227","text":"• Recurrencias más comunes en pacientes con MEN1: 21% a 10 y 20 años,\\Ncomparado con 5% y 7% sin MEN1 (p<0.001) (8).","guid":"5BA_GUGF3E4XmqaoUrjiWw","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"227","text":"• Insulinoma maligno: recurrencia en 2 de 4 pacientes asintomáticos\\Npor ≥6 meses tras la operación inicial (4 y 9 años).","guid":"FqnPHkHmUl21gZD6wQ6dCQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"237","parent":"215","text":"• Supervivencia\\Ndel paciente:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"238","parent":"237","text":"• Supervivencia general similar a la de la población general.","guid":"8PHo1gU22UFSfWEzrBVYvg","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"237","text":"• Supervivencia peor en pacientes con insulinomas malignos, en pacientes\\Nmayores y en aquellos diagnosticados tempranamente (1927-1986) (8).","guid":"tB3G6JOsQcDUzmGNiUQ2fQ","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"237","text":"• Insulinoma maligno: curso prolongado de la enfermedad.","guid":"gu5ep6x9vu3cvbLLkkTmRg","children":[]},{"id":"241","parent":"237","text":"• Serie NIH (10 pacientes tratados por insulinoma metastásico en 20 años):\\N9 vivos a largo plazo (hasta 25 años), 3 con metástasis hepáticas (47).","guid":"wOdddsJX5psna13oaLcnwg","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"237","text":"• Enfermedad metastásica desarrollada entre 4-12 años tras diagnóstico inicial.","guid":"3wZrxjnwQhIE3nluDsFAUQ","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"237","text":"• Métodos de tratamiento para controlar hipoglucemia: embolización, diazóxido, ablación\\Npor radiofrecuencia, cirugía de reducción radical, verapamilo, octreotida, quimioterapia.","guid":"B9_mH_gSDmBhfUeqGrGgVg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"244","parent":"0","text":"Terapia médica para controlar la\\Nhipoglucemia sintomática","guid":"tHHzdIYb1p1-PLTXJ_Q-0A","children":[{"id":"245","parent":"244","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"246","parent":"245","text":"• Insulinoma no detectado durante\\Nexploración pancreática.","guid":"92i-vyPfYfRlVN2QeZMe4A","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"245","text":"• Pacientes no candidatos a\\Ncirugía o que optan en contra.","guid":"aBKvWu6jGLLSWGKrqdRKzA","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"245","text":"• Enfermedad metastásica irresecable.","guid":"qyqhbfL9lGCMY-K7uPEe1A","children":[]}]},{"id":"249","parent":"244","text":"• Opciones terapéuticas para prevenir\\Nhipoglucemia sintomática:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"250","parent":"249","text":"• Diazóxido:","guid":"oegt0oZE6vcpT-xlpGHZKA","children":[{"id":"251","parent":"250","text":"• Dosis divididas hasta 1200 mg/día.","guid":"TUubA6iIOHNY0Kz8XU6PgQ","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"250","text":"• Disminuye secreción de insulina.","guid":"XGLOXrLDjjxCtXHbMR29oQ","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"250","text":"• Agente preferido para terapia médica (47-49).","guid":"JFCtmPSqZ90wBVGX-lGw7w","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"250","text":"• Efectos adversos: hirsutismo, edema marcado\\N(requiere diuréticos de asa en dosis altas).","guid":"mjtIoVn2PTtUkjp_mjlllQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"255","parent":"249","text":"• Octreotida:","guid":"SHaae9oYw5BDameDtMVXSA","children":[{"id":"256","parent":"255","text":"• Análogo de somatostatina.","guid":"brYbmi8XLrdV0JtB3f7pgQ","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"255","text":"• Inhibe secreción de GH, TSH, insulina, y glucagón.","guid":"jYX0z_J7R0-Rqm8XxzmCFQ","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"255","text":"• Eficaz para controlar síntomas de glucagonomas,\\NVIPomas, y tumores carcinoides.","guid":"vY8BfuJKP57TzfEJ6AJqJw","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"255","text":"• Eficacia menos predecible para síntomas\\Nrelacionados con insulinomas (47,50-53).","guid":"QMJgyBmeNhAomTV5vBDvmg","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"255","text":"• Opción razonable para hipoglucemia persistente refractaria a diazóxido.","guid":"fLI1AsujodCh_OPUFmCmYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"261","parent":"249","text":"• Lanreotida:","guid":"NtyB9frG-GO4cg95pCRLNg","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"• Análogo de somatostatina similar a octreotida.","guid":"MZXssUvf5dniQEi20IdMrA","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"261","text":"• Disponible en forma de depósito de acción prolongada (lanreotida SR).","guid":"UYDEbCkMa3XSD7Bu2PIPiw","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"261","text":"• Eficacia clínica similar a octreotida.","guid":"aUrMDZhnwbEW-nMkIhZ7cA","children":[]}]},{"id":"265","parent":"249","text":"• Verapamilo:","guid":"zzwubiUFw5BWTC-bcw2-wA","children":[{"id":"266","parent":"265","text":"• Utilizado con cierto éxito (47).","guid":"u8LQro5fiOrZIqpbebhCGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"267","parent":"249","text":"• Fenitoína:","guid":"DTS8oxvczaKL7GyWi6aLfg","children":[{"id":"268","parent":"267","text":"• Utilizada con cierto éxito (54).","guid":"jTk2y5TUJtXR1IpnzTZ_DA","children":[]}]},{"id":"269","parent":"249","text":"• Everolimus:","guid":"dUdkxI9TzFzewbPRL9SEpw","children":[{"id":"270","parent":"269","text":"• Inhibidor de mTOR.","guid":"K-a5CALD7TNsz6JmQYRMwQ","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"269","text":"• Respuesta en casos refractarios\\Nsegún datos limitados.","guid":"02FQWnwWqPsjvn8XtaK4YQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"272","parent":"0","text":"Terapia de radiación y\\Ntratamientos dirigidos al hígado\\Npara enfermedad metastásica","guid":"teFlS_PT33Wwg5xIQ92g9A","children":[{"id":"273","parent":"272","text":"• Radioterapia\\Nexterna (EBRT):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"274","parent":"273","text":"• Experiencia limitada en tumores\\Nde células de los islotes.","guid":"yN8f8iPY6mXgDUIAW7z4HQ","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"273","text":"• Anteriormente considerados\\Nradiorresistentes.","guid":"NAEiZTJRrdJ_mEKkHZz_HQ","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"273","text":"• Datos de casos y series pequeñas sugieren altas tasas de paliación de síntomas y\\Ncontrol local en pacientes no candidatos a resección quirúrgica (55-58).","guid":"WeR8Ktq8-e3WA3aggGdaHg","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"273","text":"• No hay datos específicos sobre control de síntomas en\\Npacientes con insulinomas sintomáticos.","guid":"iqWHwM3jXkNsPQC1BeFMag","children":[]}]},{"id":"278","parent":"272","text":"• Terapia dirigida al hígado para\\Nenfermedad metastásica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"279","parent":"278","text":"• Resección\\Nhepática:","guid":"DRAXE30Wv2RJ4hdCMMp_5g","children":[{"id":"280","parent":"279","text":"• Indicada en ausencia de afectación bilobular difusa, función hepática comprometida,\\No metástasis extrahepáticas extensas (ej., pulmonares, peritoneales).","guid":"8qASBCL-1X0EjZR30Ay7PQ","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"279","text":"• No cura la mayoría de los casos, pero permite supervivencia prolongada.","guid":"8uwVhNIE3wFYgreVXx6iIw","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"279","text":"• Considerar solo en pacientes con un número limitado de\\Nmetástasis hepáticas y con intención curativa.","guid":"YH0-6CB8WqbXFyQTt03f-w","children":[]}]},{"id":"283","parent":"278","text":"• Embolización de la\\Narteria hepática:","guid":"GWnKQyu3nYJIonPxoOKK7g","children":[{"id":"284","parent":"283","text":"• Metástasis hepáticas derivan la mayor parte de su\\Nsuministro de sangre de la arteria hepática.","guid":"vYDubS1LHr0uJNVM2bXKLw","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"283","text":"• Embolización busca inducir necrosis de metástasis con\\Ndaño mínimo al parénquima hepático normal.","guid":"yiarseZN3WEinx2q7I4DAQ","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"283","text":"• Técnica paliativa para metástasis hepáticas sintomáticas\\Nen pacientes no candidatos a resección.","guid":"Uxt1YE0xHWcliHO10LWIWw","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"283","text":"• Tasa de respuesta >50% (disminución de\\Nsecreción hormonal o regresión radiográfica).","guid":"kzoQjOF8xzm3Gl3XxyHjZg","children":[]}]},{"id":"288","parent":"278","text":"• Ablación por radiofrecuencia\\N(RFA) y crioblación:","guid":"VvSu_27qtq7JyFmqAdiFCA","children":[{"id":"289","parent":"288","text":"• Tratamiento de enfermedad hepática predominante.","guid":"BUvyXv0iyN-ZmrYUJggRDQ","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"288","text":"• Menor morbilidad que resección hepática o embolización.","guid":"AQhWd00HrZZyAwhRSKy6gw","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"288","text":"• Aplicable solo a lesiones pequeñas, eficacia a largo plazo incierta.","guid":"WEwTz6Y0WKCpLt-6T3y9wA","children":[]}]},{"id":"292","parent":"278","text":"• Radioembolización:","guid":"FhnDhd4rKmYfooq8lIVrCQ","children":[{"id":"293","parent":"292","text":"• Uso de isótopos radiactivos (ej., itrio-90 [90-Y])\\Nunidos a microesferas de vidrio o resina.","guid":"gbQyVMQ0t-UJRT3aqc9mzw","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"292","text":"• Entrega selectiva al tumor a través de la arteria hepática.","guid":"mmb0xA4MuPwHwjEapAc5cQ","children":[]},{"id":"295","parent":"292","text":"• Beneficio limitado; un informe de caso mostró mejoría de\\Nhipoglucemia refractaria por tres meses (59).","guid":"Jg2MwAkIb8aCTvWU2BU-gg","children":[]}]},{"id":"296","parent":"278","text":"• Trasplante\\Nde hígado:","guid":"Reiqp4XGpgnWopcIRp7IfA","children":[{"id":"297","parent":"296","text":"• Número reducido de pacientes con enfermedad metastásica aislada en\\Nhígado tratados con trasplante ortotópico de hígado (OLT).","guid":"wSDmyAi1QxQYmda8Linv4A","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"296","text":"• Datos insuficientes para juzgar si se ha logrado una cura completa.","guid":"nByJWTU4pCPSs9-nYWjASQ","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"296","text":"• Disponibilidad limitada de órganos donantes\\Nrestringe la investigación de este procedimiento.","guid":"Zj-ibR5pna2yPgjMqScVPQ","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"296","text":"• Considerado un enfoque investigacional para tumores de\\Ncélulas de los islotes metastásicos, incluyendo insulinoma.","guid":"QHduLunrlngwAEBYNlFYFg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"301","parent":"0","text":"Quimioterapia y enfoques\\Nnovedosos de tratamiento","guid":"F0UFZYStGbOCopx_Iaib2g","children":[{"id":"302","parent":"301","text":"• Quimioterapia\\Nsistémica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"303","parent":"302","text":"• Experiencia limitada.","guid":"Ii914Av-Z0cfz_tunyGG6w","children":[]},{"id":"304","parent":"302","text":"• Régimen tradicional: estreptozocina y doxorrubicina.","guid":"DotPZWhqGZqv_Krb5NzQ_Q","children":[]},{"id":"305","parent":"302","text":"• Tasa de respuesta objetiva inicial reportada: hasta 69%\\Npara tumores de células de los islotes metastásicos.","guid":"eqy8hVxZoSsnGVMVz2pcrA","children":[]},{"id":"306","parent":"302","text":"• Tasa de respuesta radiológica real: 10-40%.","guid":"Q6R9ns9RwdXEvgnU6GZ3yw","children":[]},{"id":"307","parent":"302","text":"• Toxicidad del régimen (náuseas, mielosupresión prolongada, insuficiencia renal)\\N→ No aceptado ampliamente como terapia de primera línea.","guid":"Nu1iYEyfZwaBQVNfbQ81xg","children":[]}]},{"id":"308","parent":"301","text":"• Temozolomida:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"309","parent":"308","text":"• Agente alquilante activo por vía oral.","guid":"3azxZfaM1z5HZfm1BI4dww","children":[]},{"id":"310","parent":"308","text":"• Actividad antitumoral demostrada.","guid":"kUASJT72Z031stqzV7jzfA","children":[]}]},{"id":"311","parent":"301","text":"• Elección de régimen de primera línea (estreptozocina/doxorrubicina\\Nvs. temozolomida) debe individualizarse:","guid":"zy172TGfePUjUlyUfgWX0Q","children":[{"id":"312","parent":"311","text":"• Conveniencia de tratamiento oral vs. intravenoso.","guid":"Csnv7bTgPjrvWfUIosGpQg","children":[]},{"id":"313","parent":"311","text":"• Estado funcional del paciente.","guid":"zcuI-wUpNJ2PmSZBwtbsWA","children":[]},{"id":"314","parent":"311","text":"• Perfil de efectos secundarios anticipado.","guid":"WOIlsEpeCIJtbk8A4lqJtQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"315","parent":"301","text":"• Enfoques terapéuticos\\Nnovedosos:","guid":"BablMc2t5EVM9Sfa01_G7g","children":[{"id":"316","parent":"315","text":"• Desarrollo impulsado por la eficacia modesta de\\Nla quimioterapia citotóxica convencional.","guid":"lC5diEyqO0RSe5cI5Zkv2w","children":[]}]},{"id":"317","parent":"301","text":"• Terapia molecular\\Ndirigida:","guid":"qztJIect6csdoXNix2kqyA","children":[{"id":"318","parent":"317","text":"• Inhibidores de tirosina quinasa de pequeñas moléculas.","guid":"pGoYiXR1L8yFoLNwrgWerw","children":[]},{"id":"319","parent":"317","text":"• Inhibidores del mTOR.","guid":"3vF_9GY1qej9yUDdwAvHiA","children":[]}]},{"id":"320","parent":"301","text":"• Terapia con radioligandos de receptores peptídicos","guid":"RhTcsw4d07uJQVT8sNpiWQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"321","parent":"0","text":"Vigilancia post-tratamiento\\Npara insulinoma maligno","guid":"E1ar5jd7csOxTQjJg99pEw","children":[{"id":"322","parent":"321","text":"• No hay guías basadas en evidencia específicas.","guid":"qQW9vwe_gTuM3n6iyIlxaw","children":[]},{"id":"323","parent":"321","text":"• Seguimiento\\Npostresección:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"324","parent":"323","text":"• 3 a 12 meses\\Npostresección:","guid":"TNxYYfmm8PmRE-Xa65n4lA","children":[{"id":"325","parent":"324","text":"• Historia clínica y examen físico.","guid":"ZdJ3hWDwbjES1SQcy_9Ztw","children":[]},{"id":"326","parent":"324","text":"• Marcadores tumorales.","guid":"TItZ1jsVKJ-Zt75JLA3T6Q","children":[]},{"id":"327","parent":"324","text":"• TC/RMN.","guid":"6MrdBJ3owOhCsH6mjnYFtg","children":[]}]},{"id":"328","parent":"323","text":"• A largo plazo:","guid":"g2DKr4HUZIzOi7NEK4YyZw","children":[{"id":"329","parent":"328","text":"• Historia clínica y examen físico con marcadores tumorales\\N(según indicado clínicamente) cada 6 a 12 meses.","guid":"TybASIf_Mb5OP7eUPOK2kA","children":[]},{"id":"330","parent":"328","text":"• Estudios de imagen según indicación clínica.","guid":"fGEqUz2AriV7HSTMAevhww","children":[]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":330,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"Insulinoma-2024-1","id":"map_793","resolved_references":[]}